<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉和卡阿终于到了猴子城的城边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们能看见猴子们围着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们溜到了沟里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴鲁在这里就好了。”巴希拉小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能做什么就做什么吧。”他抬头看着天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当那朵云彩挡住月亮的时候，我要到露台上去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“祝你好运。”卡阿小声说，“我去西墙那边。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完，他就爬走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们还在吹牛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利看见天黑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他听到了什么声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是巴希拉轻轻踩踏露台的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“成功了！”他心想，“我的计划成功了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹咆哮了一声，冲到了前面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他左右出击，攻击猴子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>受惊的动物们又怕又气，大声嚎叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，一只猴子踢了巴希拉一脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有一个进攻者！”她喊道，“大家抓住他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一群猴子围住了巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又咬又挠，又撕又拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同时，有两只猴子抓住了毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把毛克利拽到寺庙的墙上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他们把他推进了圆顶上的一个洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果是人类养大的男孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>掉到寺庙地上，会受伤的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127712</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但毛克利按照巴鲁教他的办法摔下去，双脚着地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呆在那儿。”一只猴子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等我们除掉你的朋友们再回来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，毛克利听得见卡阿的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上发出蛇的叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>废墟里有别的蛇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们嘶嘶地回应他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“站住，小兄弟。请不要踩我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利尽可能一动不动地站着，看着洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他听到了巴希拉激烈的大战声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴鲁一定也在这里。”毛克利想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉不会自己来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，现在巴希拉可以让我帮帮忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174780</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到蓄水池那边去，巴希拉。”毛克利喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“到有水的地方去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉听见毛克利的喊声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是万幸啊！”巴希拉边想边向蓄水池冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类孩子很安全！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，传来一声大喊，是巴鲁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴希拉！我在这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老熊气喘吁吁地爬上露台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他直立双腿，伸出了双爪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他开始打猴子们。啪！啪！啪！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利听见撞击声，接着是落水声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223460</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226366</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉跑进蓄水池里去了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们不会跟着他进去的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑豹气喘吁吁，头刚刚露出水面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们气得在台阶上上蹿下跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们做好了准备，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果巴希拉出来帮助巴鲁，他们就扑向巴希拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卡阿在哪儿？”巴希拉想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条蟒蛇走了吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬起滴水的下巴，发出蛇叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡阿花了很长时间才越过西墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他卷曲、伸直身体，以保证身体的每个部位都用得上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>同时，巴鲁打了几只猴子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蝙蝠在他们上面飞来飞去，带来了大战的消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，大象哈提大喊，叫醒了鸟儿们和更多的猴子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>森林动物们开始飞快地向猴子城跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，卡阿到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他准备来一个致命一击。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>蟒蛇的第一次进攻击中了巴鲁周围猴子的中心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不需要再进攻了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为猴子们立刻四散开来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是卡阿！”他们喊道，“快跑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>